遊詩人，準備過個充滿交際的生活。“ <BR> </font><P><P><i></i></TD></TR></TABLE></TD></TR></TABLE><TABLE BORDER=0 WIDTH=95%><TR><TD ALIGN=LEFT></TD><TD ALIGN=RIGHT><A HREF=http://pub3.ezboard.com/fdsafclass.showMessage?topicID=97.topic><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1><< Prev Topic</FONT></A> &nbsp;<A HREF=http://pub3.ezboard.com/fdsafclass.showMessage?topicID=94.topic><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>Next Topic >></FONT></A> </TD></TR></TABLE><BR><TABLE WIDTH=95% BORDER=0><TR><TD><A HREF=http://pub3.ezboard.com/fdsafclass.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=95.topic&index=1><IMG SRC=http://www.everquest.com.tw/images/reply.gif border=0></A></TD><TD><A HREF=http://pub3.ezboard.com/fdsafclass.emailToFriend?topicID=95.topic><IMG SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/images/email.gif BORDER=0 ALT="Email This To a Friend"></A><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=2>&nbsp;Email This To a Friend</FONT><BR><A HREF=http://pub3.ezboard.com/fdsafclass.threadControl?topicID=95.topic><IMG SRC=http://www.everquest.com.tw/images/control.gif BORDER=0 ALT="Topic Control Image"></A><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=2>&nbsp;&nbsp;Topic Commands (Moderator only)</FONT><BR><A HREF=http://pub3.ezboard.com/fdsafclass.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=95.topic><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=2>Subscribe</FONT></A>  <FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=2>Click to receive email notification of replies</FONT><BR><A HREF=http://pub3.ezboard.com/fdsafclass.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=95.topic><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=2>Unsubscribe</FONT></A>  <FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=2>Click to stop receiving email notification of replies</FONT><BR></TD><TD></TD></TR><TR><TD COLSPAN=3 ALIGN=CENTER><BR><FORM ACTION=http://pub3.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum METHOD=POST><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=2>Jump to: </FONT><SELECT NAME=forumName><OPTION VALUE=dsafugannouncement>議事廳公佈事項(Announcement)<OPTION VALUE=dsafhqforstuff>站務人員討論區(For Staff)<OPTION VALUE=dsafqsysop>站務討論(SYSOP)<OPTION VALUE=dsafdeleted>刪除文章(Deleted)<OPTION